{"about_the_game":"PLOT4 is a drawing game using colored blocks as<br />\r\nsmall bricks to build stylized geometric shapes.<br />\r\nIf we build a brick house we start from the bottom up<br />\r\nplacing the new bricks on top of the others, layer by layer.<br />\r\nInstead in PLOT4 we start from a drawing plane, in front of us as<br />\r\na vertical wall, then we add a parallel plane every time<br />\r\nwe want to advance. The quantity of vertical planes used<br />\r\nbecomes the dimension of three-dimensional depth but also becomes<br />\r\nthe fourth temporal dimension in a succession of levels.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhat happens after you place so many colored blocks?<br />\r\nYou can move freely with the 3D camera in the virtual space and<br />\r\nobserve your three-dimensional drawing.<br />\r\nYou can also start an automatic succession of parallel planes,<br />\r\ncreating a sequence of rapidly moving blocks, or an infinite loop of<br />\r\nviews in which the planes return to the beginning and<br />\r\nrepeat continuously.<br />\r\nChoosing among the different options available to you, you can also<br />\r\nask to draw a single plane at a time, in temporal succession,<br />\r\ncreating a cinematic effect where each plane becomes the frame<br />\r\nof a short film.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBefore purchasing the game, watch all the videos on this store page<br />\r\nbecause they will be useful to understand the examples of the game and how it works.<br />\r\nTo use PLOT4 with ease, you will need some training time<br />\r\nto learn the controls and to get used to drawing in four dimensions.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395070/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738098090","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395070/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738098090","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395070/8027c3a3848c66c99e7a49ea867cf795e74